      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis sub-model selection must be justified for the flow regime.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating machinery hemolysis simulations. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) applied consistently with prior FDA benchmark studies."
    },
