      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used for validation must be representative of clinical device population.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. FDA benchmark experimental data collected using standardized bovine blood preparations per ASTM F1841. Sample representativeness for human clinical use is acknowledged as a limitation managed at higher MRL."
