    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error quantified at 3.2% GCI, below the 5% threshold. RHI predictions fall within experimental uncertainty at all five operating points. Six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 framework. The model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
